<div class="home-container">
  <h1>Listen and Learn <br> Language Fun for Everyone!</h1>
  <div class="header-details">
    <p>
    Turbocharge your language learning 100% free! Practice by listening and writing what you hear. Improve your listening, speaking, grammar, and vocabulary all at once!
    </p>
    <p>
    We have hundreds of exercises in different difficulties and add new ones daily!
    </p>
    <div>
      <%= link_to passages_path, class: 'link-button' do %>
        Start Now!
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="line-separator">
  </div>
  <div class="learning-methods-container">
    <h2>
    Choose from over 20+ topics and real life situations to learn a language.
    </h2>
    <p class="learning-methods-text">
    We recommend following these simple steps to begin learning at the speed of light.
    </p>
    <div class="learning-method-group">
      <div class="learning-method-item">
        <h3>1. Listen</h3>
        <img src="/images/listen-man.png">
        <p>
        Listening supercharges language learning by exposing you to real-world speech, helping you pick up vocabulary, grammar, pronunciation, and flow naturally.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="learning-method-item">
        <h3>2. Write</h3>
        <img src="/images/typing-woman.png">
        <p>
        Writing strengthens language learning by reinforcing vocabulary, grammar, and sentence structure through active practice.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="learning-method-group">
      <div class="learning-method-item">
        <h3>3. Correct Mistakes</h3>
        <img src="/images/correct.png">
        <p>
        Correcting mistakes accelerates language learning by turning errors into valuable lessons.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="learning-method-item">
        <h3>4. Read</h3>
        <img src="/images/speak-woman.png">
        <p>
        Reading out loud improves language learning by enhancing pronunciation, fluency, and listening skills. It helps you internalize the languageâ€™s rhythm while boosting speaking confidence.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="learning-method-group">
      <div class="learning-method-item">
        <h3>5. Recall (Flashcards coming soon)</h3>
        <img src="/images/thinking-man.png">
        <p>
        Creating flashcards for spaced repetition helps language learning by reinforcing vocabulary and concepts at optimal intervals. This method boosts long-term memory retention while making learning more efficient and personalized.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="line-separator">
  </div>
  <div class="home-exercises-container">
    <h2>
      Exercises
    </h2>
    <div>
      We have hundreds of exercises in the form of passages. Passages are split up into different topics with difficulty levels ranging from Basic and A1, to C3 and Native! Below are few of the 20+ different topic you will find here. New passages are added daily!
    </div>
    <div>
      <div>
        World News
      </div>
      <div>
        Sports
      </div>
      <div>
        Health
      </div>
      <div>
        Daily Routine
      </div>
      <div>
        Career
      </div>
      <div>
        Conversations
      </div>
      <div>
        Dating
      </div>
      <div>
        Food
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="line-separator">
  </div>

  <div class="home-faq-container">
    <h2>Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <%= render partial: 'faq/partials/faqs' %>
  </div>
</div>

